<asp:Content ID="Content1" ContentPlaceHolderID="demo" runat="Server">
    <p>
        EO.Slider and EO.RangeSlider allows you to select a value or a value range on a scale. Key features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Supports all popular browsers: IE 6.0+, FireFox 1.0+, Mozilla 1.3+, Opera 7.2+,
            Safari 1.3+ and Chrome; </li>
        <li>Works with all major ASP.NET versions since ASP.NET 2.0; </li>
        <li>Supports both pointing device (mouse) and touch device. On a touch device, user
            can select the value by "dragging" the thumb; </li>
        <li>Fully customizable value range, small interval, big interval, large tick mark image,
            small tick mark image, track unselected portion image and track selected portion
            image; </li>
        <li>Supports both horizontal and vertical sliders; </li>
        <li>Support labels at arbitrary values; </li>
    </ul>
</asp:Content>
